flowchart TD

  Start["Operator utterance"] --> CompileIntent["LLM / deterministic compile_operator_intent<br>utterance → OperatorIntent schema"]
  CompileIntent --> VerifyIntent["IntentVerifier<br>semantic preservation signals<br>superlative / ordinal / metric / negation / cardinality"]
  VerifyIntent --> RequestPlan["RequestPlan compiler<br>objective → typed dependency graph<br>grounding / claims / selector / task / answer"]
  RequestPlan --> ContractLoad["Substrate contract manifest<br>primitive pre/postconditions<br>claims / frames / units<br>safety / authority / validators"]
  ContractLoad --> Readiness["ReadinessGraph<br>evaluate each plan node against<br>CapabilityRegistry + contracts + Memory + ActiveClaims + SceneModel"]

  Readiness -->|needs clarification| Ask["Ask one narrow clarification<br>store pending RequestPlan"]
  Ask --> Start

  Readiness -->|missing authority| AskAuthority["Ask / require operator authority<br>do not execute"]
  AskAuthority --> Start

  Readiness -->|contract mismatch| ContractBlock["Report failed primitive contract<br>frame / unit / claim / validation issue"]
  ContractBlock --> Start

  Readiness -->|stale or missing claims| RefreshClaims["Refresh / compute ActiveClaims<br>using registered grounding primitives"]
  RefreshClaims --> Readiness

  Readiness -->|synthesizable missing primitive| Propose["Explain gap + proposal<br>operator approves synthesis"]
  Propose -->|approved| Synthesize["Synthesize + validate + register primitive"]
  Synthesize --> Readiness
  Propose -->|rejected / redirect| Start

  Readiness -->|unsupported or missing skills| Refuse["Report blocking plan node<br>do not execute"]
  Refuse --> Start

  Readiness -->|answer query| Answer["Compose answer from SceneModel / grounding claims / operator claims"]
  Answer --> Start

  Readiness -->|memory update| MemoryUpdate["Write operator claim or update episodic memory<br>(concept_teach → KnowledgeBase,<br>delivery_target → OperationalMemory.knowledge,<br>only declared writes)"]
  MemoryUpdate --> Start

  Readiness -->|ready task| Materialize["Materialize TaskRequest + Procedure<br>from grounded RequestPlan"]
  Materialize --> CompileProc["LLM compile_procedure if needed<br>TaskRequest → Procedure"]
  CompileProc --> Prewarm["JIT prewarm<br>compile/cache templates before render"]

  Prewarm --> Cache["PlanCache<br>ProcedureRecipe<br>SensePlanTemplate<br>SkillPlanTemplate"]

  Cache --> Preflight["Contract preflight<br>validation hooks / shadow checks<br>no unsafe schema-only execution"]
  Preflight --> Loop["Runtime control loop<br>NO LLM during render"]

  Loop --> EF["Cortex creates EvidenceFrame"]
  EF --> SenseCache{"Sense template cached?"}
  SenseCache -->|hit| SenseRun["Sense executes cached template<br>latest observation → WorldModelSample"]
  SenseCache -->|miss outside render| SenseCompile["LLM compile_sense_plan<br>then cache"]
  SenseCompile --> SenseRun

  SenseRun --> Evidence["OperationalEvidence + Percepts"]
  Evidence --> CortexUpdate["Cortex updates Claims / State / Provenance"]

  CortexUpdate --> Contract["Cortex issues ExecutionContract"]
  Contract --> SkillCache{"Skill template cached?"}
  SkillCache -->|hit| SpineRun["Spine executes cached template<br>latest percepts/state → action"]
  SkillCache -->|miss outside render| SkillCompile["LLM compile_skill_plan<br>then cache"]
  SkillCompile --> SpineRun

  SpineRun --> Report["ExecutionReport + ExecutionContext"]
  Report --> Done{"Task complete?"}

  Done -->|no| Loop
  Done -->|yes| Memory["End-of-episode memory update<br>durable Knowledge + episodic memory"]
  Memory --> End["Finish"]
